#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:67
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "The KDE Forums offer users, developers and people interested in KDE a "
#| "place to help each other, discuss KDE-related topics and exchange ideas. "
#| "You can find <ulink url=\"http://forum.kde.org/viewforum.php?f=14/"
#| "\">Tutorials &amp; Tips</ulink> in the forum."
msgid ""
"The &kde; Forums offer users, developers and people interested in &kde; a "
"place to help each other, discuss &kde;-related topics and exchange ideas. "
"You can find <ulink url=\"https://forum.kde.org/viewforum.php?f=14/"
"\">Tutorials &amp; Tips</ulink> in the forum."
msgstr ""
"Les forums de KDE offrent aux utilisateurs, développeurs et personnes "
"intéressées par KDE un lieu où s'entraider, discuter de sujets relatifs à "
"KDE et échanger des idées. Vous pouvez trouver des <ulink url=\"http://forum."
"kde.org/viewforum.php?f=14/\">tutoriels et des trucs et astuces</ulink> dans "
"le forum."

